  author = "R. F Kiefl and G. D. Morris and P. Amaudruz and R. Baartman and J. Behr and J. H. Brewer and J. Chakhalian and S. Daviel and J. Doornbos and S. Dunsiger and S. R Kreitzman and T. Kuo and C. D. P. Levy and R. Miller and M. Olivo and R. Poutissou and G. W. Wight and A. Zelenski",
